*Osam* puta sam ponovio pitanje. (I repeated the question eight times.)

Imao sam *osam* godina kada je to desilo. (I was eight years old when that happened.)

Koliko imaš *osam* u kući? (How many do you have at home?)

Ona je pozvala *osam* prijatelja na proslavu. (She invited eight friends to the celebration.)

Učenici su imali *osam* zadataka za večeras. (The students had eight tasks for tonight.)

Dobio sam *osam* poena. (I got eight points.)

*Osam* je moj srećan broj. (Eight is my lucky number.)

*Osam* je najveći broj. (Eight is the biggest number.)

Ona je nosila *osam* karata. (She was carrying eight cards.)